# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:14
translate french mari2_cfee0164:

    # fr "Hey honey, how are you doing today?"
    fr "Salut chérie, comment ça va aujourd’hui ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:15
translate french mari2_b25a5732:

    # "She looks like she isn't in a great mood today. Not her normal flirty self."
    "Elle a l’air d’être de mauvaise humeur aujourd’hui. Elle n’est pas aussi coquette que d’habitude."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:18
translate french mari2_8bbaf6cc:

    # fr "Good. Let me know if you need anything."
    fr "Bien. Dis-moi si tu as besoin de quoi que ce soit."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:22
translate french mari2_eaf17857:

    # fr "Oh I'm okay. Thanks for asking though."
    fr "Oh, ça va. Merci de demander quand même."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:23
translate french mari2_7d52d223:

    # fr "Let me know if you need anything."
    fr "Dis-moi si tu as besoin de quoi que ce soit."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:26
translate french mari2_2d8fae6e:

    # "She goes off to help other customers and I finish my meal."
    "Elle part s'occuper d'autres clients et je termine mon repas."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:27
translate french mari2_89a46191:

    # "When I get up to put a tip on the table and leave, she walks back over to me."
    "Quand je me lève pour laisser un pourboire sur la table et partir, elle revient vers moi."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:32
translate french mari2_88c41b9d:

    # fr "Hey, could I ask a favor of you?"
    fr "Salut, je peux te demander un service ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:33
translate french mari2_82701f42:

    # pc "Sure, what's up?"
    pc "Bien sûr, qu'est-ce qu'il y a ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:34
translate french mari2_213affe7:

    # fr "Could you give me a ride home? My ride sort of flaked on me and I don't have any other way."
    fr "Tu pourrais me ramener chez moi ? Celui qui devait me ramener m'a laissé tomber et je n'ai pas d'autre moyen."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:40
translate french mari2_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_thankyousomuch.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_thankyousomuch.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:41
translate french mari2_eb69738f:

    # fr "Oh my God, thank you so much."
    fr "Oh mon Dieu, merci beaucoup."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:42
translate french mari2_2adb5a8d:

    # fr "Give me just a second and I'll get my things."
    fr "Donne-moi juste une seconde, je vais chercher mes affaires."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:46
translate french mari2_0d357970:

    # fr "Oh, I can give you gas money, that's not a problem."
    fr "Oh, je peux te donner de l'argent pour l'essence, ça ne pose pas de problème."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:49
translate french mari2_62b6a0da:

    # "She pulls $10 out of her roll of tips and hands it to me."
    "Elle sort 10 dollars de sa liasse de pourboires et me les tend."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:50
translate french mari2_f974fab7:

    # fr "Is that good?"
    fr "Ça te va ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:51
translate french mari2_0b6a83d2:

    # pc "It'll do."
    pc "Ça ira."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:54
translate french mari2_3438dbc6:

    # fr "Great. Give me just a second and I'll get my things."
    fr "Super. Donne-moi juste une seconde, je vais chercher mes affaires."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:59
translate french mari2_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mari_really.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_really.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:60
translate french mari2_4d187fb5:

    # fr "Really? That's all you're interested in?"
    fr "Vraiment ? C'est tout ce qui t'intéresse ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:61
translate french mari2_43e318dc:

    # fr "I mean, maybe we'll get there eventually, but I'm not going to pay you for a ride with sex."
    fr "Je veux dire, on y arrivera peut-être un jour, mais je ne vais pas te payer pour un trajet en échange de sexe."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:62
translate french mari2_78bddb29:

    # fr "I'm not a fucking hooker, and if that's all you're interested in, you're going to be real disappointed."
    fr "Je ne suis pas une putain de prostituée, et si c'est tout ce qui t'intéresse, tu vas être vraiment déçu."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:63
translate french mari2_f12af312:

    # fr "I thought you were a good guy."
    fr "Je pensais que t'étais un type bien."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:64
translate french mari2_a2c38898:

    # pc "I'm sorry, you're right. I didn't mean to offend you."
    pc "Je suis désolé, tu as raison. Je ne voulais pas te vexer."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:65
translate french mari2_4d330eb0:

    # fr "It's fine. I'll find somebody else to give me a ride."
    fr "C'est bon. Je trouverai quelqu'un d'autre pour m'emmener."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:66
translate french mari2_c4ac6d6e:

    # pc "No really, I'm sorry. I'll give you a ride, it's no problem."
    pc "Non, vraiment, je suis désolé. Je t'emmène, ça ne pose aucun problème."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:67
translate french mari2_67fd9cd9:

    # fr "Really?"
    fr "Vraiment ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:68
translate french mari2_b65a9522:

    # pc "Yeah. Seriously. I'm sorry."
    pc "Oui. Sérieusement. Je suis désolé."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:71
translate french mari2_99a094ef:

    # fr "Alright then, you're forgiven. Give me just a second and I'll go get my things."
    fr "Très bien, je te pardonne. Donne-moi juste une seconde, je vais chercher mes affaires."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:74
translate french mari2_b5cd2a72:

    # "She walks to the back and returns a few minutes later."
    "Elle se dirige vers l'arrière et revient quelques minutes plus tard."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:75
translate french mari2_d71a2aa1:

    # "Jackson stops her with a hand on her shoulder."
    "Jackson l'arrête en posant une main sur son épaule."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:79
translate french mari2_531c37ba:

    # jk "You gonna be okay, honey?"
    jk "Ça va aller, ma chérie ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:80
translate french mari2_a6099dab:

    # fr "Yeah, he's going to give me a ride home."
    fr "Oui, il va me ramener chez moi."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:81
translate french mari2_8173ea67:

    # "Jackson looks at me as if he is memorizing every feature of my face."
    "Jackson me regarde comme s'il voulait mémoriser chaque trait de mon visage."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:82
translate french mari2_6488aae0:

    # jk "Alright, you just be careful."
    jk "D'accord, fais attention à toi."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:83
translate french mari2_3d89522a:

    # fr "I will. See you tomorrow."
    fr "Je ferai attention. À demain."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:84
translate french mari2_305b4486:

    # "With that, she gives him a quick hug and then walks over to meet me at the front door."
    "Sur ces mots, elle lui donne une petite accolade puis se dirige vers moi à la porte d'entrée."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:88
translate french mari2_9e7f945c:

    # fr "Ready."
    fr "Je suis prête."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:89
translate french mari2_70536ac6:

    # pc "Alright, let's go."
    pc "Très bien, allons-y."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:94
translate french mari2_1c8790ac:

    # "I lead her out to the car and we get in and start down the road."
    "Je la conduis jusqu'à la voiture, nous montons à bord et prenons la route."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:95
translate french mari2_de1f8e81:

    # fr "My place is a little out of town on Highway 69."
    fr "Je vis un peu en dehors de la ville, sur l’autoroute 69."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:96
translate french mari2_f3f37acf:

    # fr "If you just follow this road for a while, I'll tell you where to turn."
    fr "Si tu suis cette route pendant un moment, je te dirai où tourner."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:97
translate french mari2_cd58ed18:

    # fr "I'm sorry I didn't tell you how far out it was. I figured that once I got in the car, you wouldn't kick me out."
    fr "Je suis désolée de ne pas t’avoir dit que c’était si loin. Je me suis dit qu’une fois dans la voiture, tu ne me mettrais pas à la porte."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:100
translate french mari2_76bd5ac0:

    # fr "Yeah, I'm sorry. You're not going to kick me out are you?"
    fr "Oui, je suis désolé. Tu ne vas pas me mettre à la porte, n’est-ce pas ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:101
translate french mari2_244880a1:

    # pc "Not this time."
    pc "Pas cette fois."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:102
translate french mari2_da9fa5f9:

    # fr "Phew!"
    fr "Ouf !"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:104
translate french mari2_c982865c:

    # fr "Well that's nice to hear."
    fr "Eh bien, ça fait plaisir à entendre."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:105
translate french mari2_2ee8f7d9:

    # fr "I honestly don't know what I would have done if you hadn't given me a ride."
    fr "Honnêtement, je ne sais pas ce que j’aurais fait si tu ne m’avais pas prise en stop."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:106
translate french mari2_ea4aaa45:

    # fr "Jackson doesn't drive anymore and he lives right next to the restaurant and Connie flaked out on me."
    fr "Jackson ne conduit plus et il habite juste à côté du restaurant, et Connie m’a laissée tomber."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:107
translate french mari2_5e87a42c:

    # pc "You don't have any other friends?"
    pc "Tu n’as pas d’autres amis ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:110
translate french mari2_37eecf83:

    # fr "Not really. I work pretty much every night and go to school during the day."
    fr "Pas vraiment. Je travaille presque tous les soirs et je vais à l’école pendant la journée."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:111
translate french mari2_be893470:

    # pc "You're going to college?"
    pc "Tu vas à l'université ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:115
translate french mari2_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/mari_yeah.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_yeah.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:116
translate french mari2_2b133d9a:

    # fr "Yeah, I mean I like working for Jackson, but I don't want to be a waitress all my life."
    fr "Oui, j'aime bien travailler pour Jackson, mais je ne veux pas être serveuse toute ma vie."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:117
translate french mari2_764b7928:

    # pc "You go to Skyhill?"
    pc "Tu vas à Skyhill ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:118
translate french mari2_b9bbe0c8:

    # fr "No I'm in the veterinarian program in Whiterock."
    fr "Non, je suis en formation de vétérinaire à Whiterock."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:119
translate french mari2_d9c0d3c2:

    # pc "Veterinarian? That's cool."
    pc "Vétérinaire ? C'est cool."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:120
translate french mari2_95ddebf0:

    # fr "Yeah, I love animals. I volunteer at the Skyhill Animal clinic on the weekend too."
    fr "Oui, j’adore les animaux. Je fais aussi du bénévolat à la clinique vétérinaire de Skyhill le week-end."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:121
translate french mari2_9f24bfc7:

    # fr "And then when I'm not doing all of that, I have to take care of the farm, so not a lot of time for friends."
    fr "Et puis, quand je ne fais pas tout ça, je dois m’occuper de la ferme, donc je n’ai pas beaucoup de temps pour mes amis."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:122
translate french mari2_b7bcaa75:

    # pc "Farm?"
    pc "Une ferme ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:123
translate french mari2_34b74c62:

    # fr "Yeah, I live on a farm. You'll see. It's coming up here on the right."
    fr "Oui, je vis dans une ferme. Tu vas voir. C’est juste là, sur la droite."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:126
translate french mari2_176d45b6:

    # fr "You're gonna want to slow down a bit. The turn is real easy to miss."
    fr "Tu vas devoir ralentir un peu. Le virage est très facile à rater."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:127
translate french mari2_57fbb466:

    # fr "Right there, behind those trees, see the mailbox?"
    fr "Juste là, derrière ces arbres, tu vois la boîte aux lettres ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:128
translate french mari2_4fe57c0e:

    # pc "Yeah, I see it."
    pc "Oui, je la vois."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:131
translate french mari2_baf3d043:

    # "I take a right onto a narrow dirt road that leads into the woods, then the woods clear away to reveal Mari's farm."
    "Je tourne à droite sur un chemin de terre étroit qui mène dans les bois, puis la forêt s'ouvre pour dévoiler la ferme de Mari."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:134
translate french mari2_0d086ddf:

    # "There are fields of crops, a barn with livestock, and an old farmhouse that looks much too big for a single person."
    "Il y a des champs de cultures, une grange avec du bétail et une vieille ferme qui semble bien trop grande pour une seule personne."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:135
translate french mari2_0ea772b8:

    # pc "You live here by yourself?"
    pc "Tu vis ici toute seule ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:137
translate french mari2_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/mari_yep.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_yep.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:138
translate french mari2_15e9c674:

    # fr "Yep, I run the whole operation."
    fr "Oui, je m'occupe de tout."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:139
translate french mari2_4b1a346a:

    # pc "Wow. I'm impressed."
    pc "Ouah. Je suis impressionné."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:140
translate french mari2_8fc70d8d:

    # fr "Thanks. It's hard work, but I love it."
    fr "Merci. C'est un travail dur, mais j'adore ça."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:141
translate french mari2_5679a178:

    # fr "Maybe you could come out during the day sometime and see the animals. I could always use a hand on the weekends."
    fr "Tu pourrais peut-être passer un jour pendant la journée pour voir les animaux. J'ai toujours besoin d'un coup de main le week-end."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:142
translate french mari2_919834dc:

    # pc "I might take you up on that."
    pc "Je vais peut-être te prendre au mot."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:147
translate french mari2_4ac7c9d1:

    # fr "Well thanks for the ride. I really appreciate it."
    fr "Bon, merci de m'avoir raccompagnée. J'apprécie vraiment."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:148
translate french mari2_0144fcab:

    # pc "It's no problem."
    pc "Pas de problème."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:149
translate french mari2_74dad108:

    # fr "You remember how to get back?"
    fr "Tu te souviens du chemin pour rentrer ?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:150
translate french mari2_560198a5:

    # pc "Yeah, I can manage."
    pc "Oui, je m'en sortirai."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:151
translate french mari2_0f1224ae:

    # fr "All right, well I better get in. Got another busy day tomorrow."
    fr "Très bien, je ferais mieux d’y aller. J’ai encore une journée chargée demain."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:152
translate french mari2_859bb5e6:

    # "She takes off her seat belt, then quickly leans over and kisses me on the cheek."
    "Elle détache sa ceinture de sécurité, puis se penche rapidement vers moi et m’embrasse sur la joue."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:155
translate french mari2_35b4ee40:

    # fr "Thanks again, you're the best."
    fr "Merci encore, tu es génial."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:157
translate french mari2_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/mari_goodnight2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_goodnight2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:158
translate french mari2_aa3809b0:

    # fr "Good night."
    fr "Bonne nuit."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:161
translate french mari2_f4ea6f40:

    # "With that, she gets out of the car and starts up towards her front porch."
    "Sur ces mots, elle sort de la voiture et se dirige vers le porche de sa maison."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:162
translate french mari2_0b673066:

    # "I wait until she gets her front door open and disappears inside before turning around and driving out of her farm and back onto the highway."
    "J'attends qu'elle ouvre sa porte d'entrée et disparaisse à l'intérieur avant de faire demi-tour, de quitter sa ferme et de rejoindre l'autoroute."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:167
translate french mari2_c755bc5c:

    # "She always seems like she is so happy, but I feel like there is a sort of sadness hidden under that cheer."
    "Elle a toujours l'air si heureuse, mais j'ai l'impression qu'une sorte de tristesse se cache derrière cette gaieté."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:168
translate french mari2_e75e84b3:

    # "I wonder why she is living on that big farm all by herself."
    "Je me demande pourquoi elle vit toute seule dans cette grande ferme."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:169
translate french mari2_efa9db91:

    # "I'll have to ask her sometime. I'd love to learn more about her."
    "Il faudra que je lui demande un jour. J'aimerais en savoir plus sur elle."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:170
translate french mari2_5cb073e5:

    # "The kiss had been nice too."
    "Le baiser était sympa aussi."

